fields.summary: iOS: Compiling the Xcode project gives warnings because TIMOB-12558 wasn't fully implemented.

comments.body: As another alternative, you could simply hide this warning with un-setting [-Warc-bridge-casts-disallowed-in-nonarc]
Sorry I meant re-open TIMOB-12558. Literally no idea how that other number appeared on my clipboard :S
